  "ARTICLE_ITEMS": "<article class=\"news-item\"><div class=\"news-img\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611162617474-5b21e879e113?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80\" alt=\"小红书爆款图文密码\"></div><div class=\"news-content\"><div class=\"news-date\">11.06.2026</div><div class=\"news-body\"><div class=\"news-text\"><h3>拆解小红书爆款图文密码：情绪价值与视觉钩子</h3><p>从封面吸睛度、标题情绪价值到正文信息密度，全方位复盘近30天内跑出的10篇百万级爆款笔记的共性特征与底层逻辑。</p></div><a href=\"#\" class=\"news-arrow\">→</a></div></div></article><article class=\"news-item\"><div class=\"news-img\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1616469829581-73993eb86b02?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80\" alt=\"B站中视频\"></div><div class=\"news-content\"><div class=\"news-date\">28.05.2026</div><div class=\"news-body\"><div class=\"news-text\"><h3>B站知识区起号全指南：从选题库到完播率优化</h3><p>在这个信息过载的时代，如何通过结构化的表达和高密度的脚本，在B站实现从0到1万粉的突破？附带数据指标分析框架。</p></div><a href=\"#\" class=\"news-arrow\">→</a></div></div></article><article class=\"news-item\"><div class=\"news-img\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80\" alt=\"数据驱动营销\"></div><div class=\"news-content\"><div class=\"news-date\">15.04.2026</div><div class=\"news-body\"><div class=\"news-text\"><h3>全域转化链路复盘：私域如何承接公域流量溢出</h3><p>单纯的涨粉不再是唯一目标，如何搭建从「流量」到「留量」的转化闭环？深入解析引流钩子设计、企业微信承接策略与自动化SOP。</p></div><a href=\"#\" class=\"news-arrow\">→</a></div></div></article><article class=\"news-item\"><div class=\"news-img\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1499750310107-5fef28a66643?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80\" alt=\"公众号内容工程\"></div><div class=\"news-content\"><div class=\"news-date\">10.03.2026</div><div class=\"news-body\"><div class=\"news-text\"><h3>公众号打开率提升30%的秘密：A/B测试与标题工程</h3><p>在算法推荐时代，公众号依然是建立深度信任的最佳阵地。通过建立标准化的选题库与标题测试模型，突破微信生态的流量瓶颈。</p></div><a href=\"#\" class=\"news-arrow\">→</a></div></div></article><article class=\"news-item\"><div class=\"news-img\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1677442136019-21780ecad995?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80\" alt=\"AI内容生产\"></div><div class=\"news-content\"><div class=\"news-date\">22.02.2026</div><div class=\"news-body\"><div class=\"news-text\"><h3>拥抱AI：如何搭建高效的自动化内容生产管线</h3><p>探讨大模型在日常新媒体运营中的实际应用场景，分享将图文与短视频脚本产出效率提升三倍的标准化SOP与提示词框架。</p></div><a href=\"#\" class=\"news-arrow\">→</a></div></div></article><article class=\"news-item\"><div class=\"news-img\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80\" alt=\"短视频创作\"></div><div class=\"news-content\"><div class=\"news-date\">05.01.2026</div><div class=\"news-body\"><div class=\"news-text\"><h3>抖音短视频底层逻辑：前三秒完播率与情绪共鸣</h3><p>拒绝无效自嗨，用数据说话。拆解短视频算法分发机制，分享如何利用「黄金三秒」钩子设计与情绪跌宕提升视频的综合数据表现。</p></div><a href=\"#\" class=\"news-arrow\">→</a></div></div></article>",
